 able to work with different mediums and have a strong design experience and understanding of each medium 3. Strong communicator - You will be responsible for crafting design content and collaterals our clients will use for their campaigns. As such, you are expected to be able to clearly articulate your concepts and and selected creative elements 4. Accountability - You will be responsible for the success of the project. We are looking for someone who is committed and highly responsible 5. Able to handle stress - You will need to manage short deadlines and also put your crisis management skills to work as a part of this role. You are expected to be able to think quickly and calmly, and execute on solutions quickly 6. Creative thinker - We expect you to showcase out-of-the-box thinking to address problems. You will also be expected to actively contribute to brainstorming sessions for pitches, proposals and projects 7. Systematic - You will be required to have a smooth creative workflow at all times ensuring efficient versioning, archiving and handover of projects to colleagues and clients 8. Design experience - We expect to see a diverse portfolio which demonstrates proficiency in the design and visualisation of unique concepts for brand campaigns, as well as artworking of banners, presentation and proposal mockups and layouts. 2D graphic, photography and photo editing skills are required. Illustration, branding and animation skills are preferred Skills Graphic Design, Detail-Oriented, Communication Skills, Time Management Compensation SGD 2,200 - 2,700 monthly ",
